01:13:44,500 --> 01:13:45,900
I have explained to you

1211
01:13:46,000 --> 01:13:48,200
that buying merchandise

1212
01:13:48,300 --> 01:13:50,100
or borrowing cash

1213
01:13:50,200 --> 01:13:52,300
or buying services

1214
01:13:52,400 --> 01:13:56,300
